name: Release 5.7.17
body:
[SW-22909](https://issues.shopware.com/issues/SW-22909) - Salutation could be deactivated now
[SW-23083](https://issues.shopware.com/issues/SW-23083) - Removes configurator option from article name after converting variant article to main article and relationships of configurator options to deleted variants.
[SW-23455](https://issues.shopware.com/issues/SW-23455) - For discounts and surcharges a record is created in the s_order_basket_attributes
[SW-23762](https://issues.shopware.com/issues/SW-23762) - The parameter -m for the sw:media:optimize command now works as intended
[SW-24545](https://issues.shopware.com/issues/SW-24545) - Improve settings and behaviour of similar products on product detail page
[SW-24778](https://issues.shopware.com/issues/SW-24778) - The release date is now shown correctly on the note
[SW-25764](https://issues.shopware.com/issues/SW-25764) - Fix not available hint for variant products with more than two options
[SW-25825](https://issues.shopware.com/issues/SW-25825) - remove "motor" from bot list for Motorola-device-compatibility
[SW-25878](https://issues.shopware.com/issues/SW-25878) - Asynchrone PluginManager Requests
[SW-25939](https://issues.shopware.com/issues/SW-25939) - Providing the information on the product detail page that the payment method has been changed.
[SW-25985](https://issues.shopware.com/issues/SW-25985) - Fixed a problem where the blog ID was non-existend after reloading the blog page with activated caching
[SW-26321](https://issues.shopware.com/issues/SW-26321) - Pre-selection of the country of delivery and dependent taxes based on the positioning of the countries
[SW-26386](https://issues.shopware.com/issues/SW-26386) - Improved snippet import
[SW-26746](https://issues.shopware.com/issues/SW-26746) - PHP 8.2 compatibility
[SW-26923](https://issues.shopware.com/issues/SW-26923) - Tax, as well as the specific price for the customer-group, are now set in order-module when adding a new position to an order
[SW-26931](https://issues.shopware.com/issues/SW-26931) - Improve PHP8 compatibility in the media module
[SW-26951](https://issues.shopware.com/issues/SW-26951) - Improve PHP8.1 compatibility of the theme cache generation [(teiling88)](https://github.com/teiling88)
[SW-26953](https://issues.shopware.com/issues/SW-26953) - Content type names are allowed to contain numbers now [(bforbird)](https://github.com/bforbird)
[SW-26954](https://issues.shopware.com/issues/SW-26954) - Update of third party dependencies
[SW-26958](https://issues.shopware.com/issues/SW-26958) - Fix deprecation in service declaration [(larsbo)](https://github.com/larsbo)
[SW-26961](https://issues.shopware.com/issues/SW-26961) - Invalidate reset password link after changing account email address.
[SW-26962](https://issues.shopware.com/issues/SW-26962) - Improve registration of CLI commands [(teiling88)](https://github.com/teiling88)
[SW-26968](https://issues.shopware.com/issues/SW-26968) - Fix creating of products with translations in the batch API
[SW-26970](https://issues.shopware.com/issues/SW-26970) - Prevent unwanted behavior when double-clicking the login button
[SW-26981](https://issues.shopware.com/issues/SW-26981) - Improve the performance of the shipping module by minimizing requests and query only necessary data
[SW-27002](https://issues.shopware.com/issues/SW-27002) - Improve PHP 8.1 compatibility [(teiling88)](https://github.com/teiling88)
[SW-27003](https://issues.shopware.com/issues/SW-27003) - Add class prefix "has--" back to modernizr [(bestit-pstandt)](https://github.com/bestit-pstandt)
[SW-27004](https://issues.shopware.com/issues/SW-27004) - Removed duplicated font folders in theme to fix installation problem on MacOS
[SW-27009](https://issues.shopware.com/issues/SW-27009) - Added configuration for devenv
[SW-27018](https://issues.shopware.com/issues/SW-27018) - Improving the caching behavior of the account page.
[SW-27019](https://issues.shopware.com/issues/SW-27019) - Changed default value from the ComboBox to an empty value [(Dominikrt)](https://github.com/Dominikrt)
[SW-27031](https://issues.shopware.com/issues/SW-27031) - Adjusted honeypot captcha
[SW-27035](https://issues.shopware.com/issues/SW-27035) - When changing the order via the backend module, the delivery country is now correctly taken into account
[SW-27055](https://issues.shopware.com/issues/SW-27055) - Performance of the order confirm page improved. In addition, attributes of discount or surcharge items are now automatically transferred from the cart to the order again

Changes: https://github.com/shopware/shopware/compare/v5.7.16...v5.7.17
